# EEE4113F_Group12_PCB - embedded software
## Overview
This directory contains the software for developing an embedded-program for the BARBIE.

## What is included
This repository includes:
- Simulation files
- Firmware
- Configuration headers

None of the generated compilation files are included.

## Installation & Dependencies
The simulation uses Python 3.13.

The firmware uses the ESP-IDF framework, flashed onto the ESP32 with the PlatformIO workflow and the ESP32's USB-JTAG interface.
